    "title": "A magnificent gift from a dear friend neither forgotten nor forsaken.",
    "description": "Consumes 2 ammo per shot. Fires a miniature Butt Stallion that explodes on impact and then splits into 3 diamond projectiles, which also detonate. Swapping to the weapon plays a neigh."
