  "notes": "It can roll with any shotgun accessory, but no prefix is shown in the name. With a vertical grip, it fires extra projectiles without increasing ammo cost, dramatically boosting damage. The split projectiles deal splash damage that scales with grenade damage bonuses, and kills from them count as grenade kills, including for Pull the Pin. Absorb shields do not absorb the explosions. Its special effect matches the SWORDSPLOSION!!!. It can only be claimed once per character.",
